{"tid":1419332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非請入","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:54:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T01:21:31.000Z","uid":121231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"68d666ed00d9d3162b09788c42d10b48c4c5aea8","tid":1419332,"uid":121231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"［手動轉貼］<br />\n致所有和理非：<br />\n街頭運動我地可能無法參與<br />\n但我相信大家都好明確見到警黑等問題<br />\n如果要增加林鄭政治成本<br />\n應該針對大財團同商家<br />\n<br />\n希望大家由今日開始 ［逢雙數日］ <br />\n針對 大財團同商家 ［罷買］ <br />\n直至政府接受民意<br />\n<br />\n購物可以去返  有參加85罷工的 商鋪<br />\n或者有明確表示支持 五大訴求既 商鋪<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n1）迫使 商家 向林鄭使壓<br />\n2）日後再有罷市 利益在前 必定會增加參加鋪頭<br />\n3）增加香港人係消費上既話事權<br />\n4）零成本 無風險<br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以分享同參加<br />\n好人一世平安"},{"pid":"e6742fc8f13a42244cd37e5bed9863c92a009e34","tid":1419332,"uid":121231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:55:40.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"4a93c0eee84f734f202448fd08471feb8547436b","tid":1419332,"uid":121231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:57:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3e5c746614de659443dec09671a65aefc838cb25","tid":1419332,"uid":121231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:02:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1fdaf84011cfe9714a404d213eb36aef9af47425","tid":1419332,"uid":121231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:13:18.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"31909cbf25fc3328e621d76e141d6ed0d57853c6","tid":1419332,"uid":121231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T01:21:31.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}